description:
Seether-Isolate And Medicate (Deluxe Edition) 320k    ak2014 What we got..Isolate and Medicate is the sixth studio album by South African post-grunge band Seether. It was released on 1 July 2014.

On 1 May, 2014, the band released the first single from the album, "Words as Weapons".

It is the first Seether album to be released on a Vinyl LP.
